<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .center {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Dear, {{name}}!</h1>
        <p>We would like to remind you that we have not received payment for the order. To process orders quickly, we require proof of payment from you immediately!</p>
     <p>Please send the payment proof via this email or through the payment method you selected when placing the order. Please make sure to include the order number as a reference on your payment proof.</p>

<p>If you have already made the payment, please disregard this message. However, if you have not made the payment yet, we would greatly appreciate your prompt action in completing the payment as soon as possible.</p>

<p>Thank you for joining us.</p>

<p>Click the button below to upload payment proof.</p>

        <div class="center">
            <a href="{{link}}" class="button">Upload Payment Proof</a>
        </div>
        <hr>
      
    </div>
</body>
</html>


 